738c4d50a5987b07cac441559.mp4?t=1764635726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437200/extras/cf5b8079637a9586f734d0c318af07b2.avif?t=1764635726\" width=650 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a future where superpowered individuals—known as Wielders—make up much of the population, crime runs rampant</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Wielder terrorist group known as the Liberators has begun a massive purge, spreading fear across society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In an age of chaos, Luna—a Wielder who longs only for peace—chooses to join the SCMF and take her place as a guardian of the people. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437200/extras/16a3c843b50dbeef8d533bdb8c69087b.avif?t=1764635726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437200/extras_big/16a3c843b50dbeef8d533bdb8c69087b.webp?t=1764635726 width=1560 height=963 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437200/extras/b7762b62da1c7db162442ccfae2afbf2.avif?t=1764635726\" width=650 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437200/extras/42d86aef64bb47f438935c279bc86e5c.avif?t=1764635726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437200/extras_big/42d86aef64bb47f438935c279bc86e5c.avif?t=1764635726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ct